      "comment": "PROTEGE (2) flew the lids and led throughout to get off the mark with his maiden win, then finished a 4 length second last start at this track over 400m (22.96). Maiden this journey but has some solid runs behind him. Rates highly here and will give a sight again. DREAMTIME MASTER (1) looks close to another win after hitting the frame in a 4 length third (22.96) in a Grade 6 at this track. Expected to feature again. AILEEN'S SHINE (8) broke from a low draw and filled a minor placing last start, beaten only a neck (25.94) behind City Of Love at Murray Bridge. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Hard to beat again. ZIPPING FONTANA (4) is another with top-three prospects.",
